. 今天写前端突然发现前端的路径也是他们俗称的臭长，明明一个 model/LoginInfo.ts 就能创建为 api/interface/LoginInfo/index.ts\r\n特别是 index.js index.ts 都是创建文件单一个 index 明明如果不是多个就叫 router.ts 就好了嘛，不知道有什么特殊的吗。 \r\n3. 我觉得有一句话我挺认同的，路径长，一个是便于管理(很多写路径规范吧，或者跟着教程学的就是这样)，一个是和语言无关，和写代码的人有关。毕竟还有的人接口前面带 I 有的人不带的。没有对错之分。","content_rendered":"<ol>\n<li>感觉很多人对 java 还停留在 j2ee 时代，不过 java 还在 jdk 还在 1.8 ，就不需要谈了。</li>\n<li>今天写前端突然发现前端的路径也是他们俗称的臭长，明明一个 model/LoginInfo.ts 就能创建为 api/interface/LoginInfo/index.ts\n特别是 index.js index.ts 都是创建文件单一个 index 明明如果不是多个就叫 router.ts 就好了嘛，不知道有什么特殊的吗。 </li>\n<li>我觉得有一句话我挺认同的，路径长，一个是便于管理(很多写路径规范吧，或者跟着教程学的就是这样)，一个是和语言无关，和写代码的人有关。毕竟还有的人接口前面带 I 有的人不带的。没有对错之分。</li>\n</ol>\n","last_modified":1652152845,"replies":36,"id":851925},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":18308,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2149,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":392716,"username":"vocaloid","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/vocaloid","website":"","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"","bio":"头像画师：诗驯","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6134/c51f/392716_mini.png?m=1566707667","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6134/c51f/392716_normal.png?m=1566707667","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6134/c51f/392716_large.png?m=1566707667","created":1552728793,"last_modified":1566707667},"last_reply_by":"forgottencoast","last_touched":1652168551,"title":"iOS 通过控制中心关闭 wifi 后，总是自动打开","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/851876","created":165214